metadata.name: Pirate Nation #1
metadata.description: Pirate Nation is a light hearted game filled with high seas adventure, treasure, and fun, unique characters. Players collect and send pirates on adventures where they collect materials for crafting, treasures, and pirate gold! Pirates gain experience and can level up from their many adventures.  The game is being developed by crypto-natives that have decades of game production experience under their belts. We're excited to release Pirate Nation to the world soon. Come join us and let's grow this world together!
